{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "request_id": "rf-suggest-edit-issue-ordering-confirmed-before-unconfirmed-001",
  "project": "radishflow",
  "task": "suggest_flowsheet_edits",
  "status": "partial",
  "requires_confirmation": true,
  "summary": "当前围绕已选中的进料流股 feed-13 与加热器 heater-4 的参数缺失问题生成候选提案；对 product-13 仅有未确认影响警告，因此不提出超出局部参数补全的改动。",
  "answers": [
    {
      "summary": "建议先补全 Cold Feed 的流量规格，再补全 Balance Heater 的出口温度目标占位，以对应当前两个直接报错对象。",
      "issues": [
        {
          "title": "feed-13 缺少流量规格",
          "severity": "error",
          "citations": [
            "diag-1",
            "flowdoc-stream-1",
            "snapshot-1"
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "heater-4 缺少出口温度控制目标",
          "severity": "error",
          "citations": [
            "diag-2",
            "flowdoc-unit-1",
            "snapshot-1"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "proposed_actions": [
        {
          "action": "candidate_edit",
          "title": "为 feed-13 添加流量规格占位",
          "target": {
            "type": "stream",
            "id": "feed-13"
          },
          "rationale": "直接诊断指出 Cold Feed 缺少流量规格；在仅补全局部缺参且不假定具体数值的前提下，可先加入可审查的规格占位。",
          "patch": {
            "spec_placeholders": {
              "flow_rate": {
                "required": true,
                "reason": "STREAM_SPEC_MISSING"
              }
            }
          },
          "risk_level": "medium",
          "requires_confirmation": true,
          "citations": [
            "diag-1",
            "flowdoc-stream-1",
            "snapshot-1"
          ]
        },
        {
          "action": "candidate_edit",
          "title": "为 heater-4 添加出口温度目标占位",
          "target": {
            "type": "unit",
            "id": "heater-4"
          },
          "rationale": "该加热器已配置为 outlet_temperature 控制模式，但缺少对应目标参数；保留现有控制模式，仅补充目标参数占位可直接回应当前错误。",
          "patch": {
            "parameter_placeholders": {
              "outlet_temperature_target_c": {
                "required": true,
                "reason": "UNIT_PARAMETER_INCOMPLETE"
              }
            }
          },
          "risk_level": "medium",
          "requires_confirmation": true,
          "citations": [
            "diag-2",
            "flowdoc-unit-1",
            "snapshot-1"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "citations": [
        "diag-1",
        "diag-2",
        "flowdoc-stream-1",
        "flowdoc-unit-1",
        "snapshot-1"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
